description: The Black Market Food Truck is a mobile gourmet deli in Buffalo specializing in unique sandwiches, soups, and sides. Everything is fast, fresh, and made from scratch. Specializing in a range of regional cuisines, the ever-changing menu keeps each meal exciting for both the customers and the cooks. With dishes ranging from Coconut-Curry Chicken Souvlaki, to Vietnamese Banh-Mi, Buffalo Chicken Arancini, Homemade Juices, and Local sodas, The Black Market Food Truck is poised to become Buffalo's premier gourmet food truck!
name: Black Market Food Truck
